    "headline": "Samsung Display CEO warns of cost pressure due to oil shock from Iran war",
    "summary": "SEOUL, March 12 (Reuters) - The CEO of Samsung Display, a ‌supplier for Apple and Samsung Electronics, ‌said on Thursday the Iran war and surging ​oil prices threaten to drive up costs of energy and raw materials. Samsung Display President & CEO Chung Yi said rapidly rising ‌oil prices ⁠are adding to the tech industry's challenges at a time when ⁠it is already grappling with soaring chip prices that are inflating the costs ​of phones, ​PCs and ​other electronics devices.",
